
Download the lates binaries form: 

<http://www.bioinformatics.babraham.ac.uk/projects/download.html#fastqc>

unzip 

    unzip fastqc_v0.11.2.zip 

change permissions

    chmod +x fastqc

And add it to you rpath... write a line simmirar to this in your `.profile` file 

    export PATH=/home/dmontaner/bin/NGS/FastQC:$PATH

